707169f-a.title: Brooklyn: Vanderbilt Ave. - Atlantic Ave.
707169f-a.text:
Vanderbilt Ave., east side, from and including Atlantic Ave., to, but not including Fulton Street. A view of two 3-story frame houses, alongside of an old public auditorium. In the background, may be seen the
steeple of St. Luke's Protestant Episcopal Church.
November 26, 1927.
P. L. 5perr.
